Imperial as in "belonging to the Star Union"</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">IMPERIAL_PRODUCTION_STASH</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">When collected, production is added to your nearest colony. Production speeds up the queued items being produced in your colony. </Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Po zebraniu twoja najbliższa kolonia otrzyma produkcję. Produkcja przyspiesza wytwarzanie obiektów umieszczonych w kolejce w twojej kolonii. </Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Collected as in "picked up by an army"</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">IMPERIAL_CRYSTAL_STASH</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Imperial Cosmite Stash</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Imperialny skład kosmitu</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Energy is an in-game resource.
